## Verdict System

```
const VerdictResult = struct {
    pass: bool,
    score: f64,        // 0.0 - 100.0
    vsa_score: f64,
    vm_score: f64,
    sdk_score: f64,
    memory_score: f64,
    perf_score: f64,
};
```

